teacher_info.about_teacher:
I have developed popular programs for online learning: 
Business Russian (levels A0-C1);
Russian for tourism employees (levels A1-A2);
Russian for a tourist trip to Russia (levels A1-A2);
Russian for bilinguals 1-4 grades (children 6-12 years old).

pro_course_detail.description:
Are you interested in Russian history, culture, cinema and literature?

We can:
watch and discuss films while practicing listening;
read and discuss fiction books while working on the text;
understand history and mentality;
explore tourist attractions.

If you are interested in a specific topic - write to me.

teacher_info.about_teacher:
What I can say about me?
- I am a qualified Russian mothertongue teacher;
- Enrolled in the Register of Sworn Interpreters and Translators;
- I have a degree in Languages for international communication and cooperation;
- I have a Master in teaching Russian for foreigners and I have the license to prepare students for the international exams TBU, TRKI-1,2,3,4 and citizenship exams;
- I have 8 years of experience;
- I always adapt the study program to the personal needs of my clients;
-   I adore my language, my job and my students! I would like to interest and inspire them. I'm always kind and patient, your success is my goal.

teacher_info.teaching_style:
I use the newest and the most effective teaching methods that can help you to obtain the maximum result in minimum time.

My individual Russian lessons are for those who want:
- learn to speak Russian at a basic or advanced level for everyday conversations;
- learn to communicate with their families and children-bilingual;
- pass TRKI international exams of any level or university exams;
- work or study in Russia (business russian);
- pass the Russian exam to obtain citizenship;
- work in all over the world with Russian clients;
- learn Russian to read the original classical literature

or for any other reason, I'm at your disposal!
